### Health
GET http://localhost:8000/api/health

### Provider health
GET http://localhost:8000/api/health/providers

### What happened
GET http://localhost:8000/api/stock/NVDA/what-happened?window=today

### Sentiment
GET http://localhost:8000/api/stock/NVDA/sentiment?window=past_week

### Research snapshot
GET http://localhost:8000/api/stock/AAPL/research-snapshot

### Stock-first ask
POST http://localhost:8000/api/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{"ticker":"AAPL","query":"What happened to Apple today?"}

### Ticker-first deep research
POST http://localhost:8000/api/research
Content-Type: application/json

{"ticker":"NVDA","question":"Analyze Nvidia as a long-term AI infrastructure company.","window":"past_month","focus":["fundamentals","earnings","filings","news","sentiment"]}

